Title: JK Chunkro 2.8 Salt Black Bloom #
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Chunkro 2.8-inch salt black breeze is a soft lure with high appeal, developed specifically for black breeze (Chinus).The complex vibrations created by its large body and various parts stimulate the predation instinct of black baits.In particular, it contains a powerful flavor made from powdered shrimp flesh, and its outstanding fish attracting power induces deep bites.

This lure not only has its voluminous arms that move the water vigorously, but its curly tail-like claws create even more complex vibrations.Invite the target with a combined action that occurs from one arm.Furthermore, the four pairs of arms attached to the body inverted hands produce fine vibrations when exposed to water flow, creating slight vibrations that can be used as "feeding" elements.

The size is 2.8 inches, packed in 6 pieces, and the price is 550 yen including tax.There are a wide variety of colors available, including Gripan Melon, Red Hatard Devil, Grape Green Flake, Red Gold Flake, Orange Gold Flake, Lip Rhizo crab, Sexy Frog Grey Grey, Mushimi Glow, Shacky Cross, UV Tortoise Jaco, Globokeh Jacket, and more.

Chunkro 2.8 inch salt blacktail breezes are effective lures in blacktail games due to their high appeal and strong flavor.

Title: JK Tide Curly 2.8 #
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Tide Curly 2.8" is a soft lure designed for light salt games, and it appeals to you with a presence that makes use of its overall length, making it ideal for checking a wide range of areas at a good tempo and exploring the route of horse mackerel migration.

The tail, which accounts for more than half of the total, flies wildly, and the action is full of life and induces eating.In addition, the tail and base of the body have been designed to optimize the ease of suction and balance between action.

The size is 2.8 inches, packed with 8 pieces, and the price is 550 yen including tax.

There are a wide variety of colors available, including Peach Sour, Glow Orange/Gold Flakes, Hinata Bean Pearl, Sparkle Sardines, Oni Glow, White-tailed Sabiki, Clear Red Flakes, Clear Holo Flakes, Chilimen Monster, Clear Prism Neon, Glow, Glow Chart, Clear Glow Crash, Isome Glow Crash, Krill Glow Crash, Sardine Glow Crash, and Sardine Glow Crash.

The Tide Curly 2.8 inch lure allows for an effective approach to your target due to its presence and vitality.

Title: JK Tide Curly 2.0 #
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Tide Curly 2.0 inch is a soft lure designed for light salt games, featuring a half-ring shape with ribs at the bottom of the body and an ultra-thin curly tail. This design creates fine vibrations and provides a strong appeal to targets such as horse mackerel and rockfish. Additionally, the body's ribs and curly tail firmly hold the water, creating moderate pull resistance, making it easier to maintain the desired range.

There are two sizes: 2.0 inches and 2.8 inches, and the 2.0 inches is a bite-sized all-rounder that can be used in any location or field, and can be used with a variety of rigs, from jig heads to carolina rigs and float rigs.

There are a wide variety of colors available, including Peach Sour, Glow Orange/Gold Flakes, Hinata Bean Pearl, Sparkle Sardines, Oni Glow, White-tailed Sabiki, Clear Red Flakes, Clear Holo Flakes, Chilimen Monster, Clear Prism Neon, Glow, Glow Chart, Clear Glow Crash, Isome Glow Crash, Krill Glow Crash, Sardine Glow Crash, and Sardine Glow Crash.

The Tide Curly 2.0 inch pack is 8 bottles and costs 550 yen including tax.

Title: JK Kibiki Binargo 2 #
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Kibikibina-Go 2 inch is a soft lure specializing in light games such as ajing and mebaring. The triangular prism-shaped body that cuts through water and the cross-tail-shaped tail section allow for a wide variety of action, from free wrapping to dirt action. In particular, when combined with a jig head with a line eye located at the rear, it is possible to easily perform a tempting dirt action.

This lure is effective not only for horse mackerel and rockfish, but also for fish eaters such as plating and buckwheat, making it an item that expands the range of light games. It is a 2-inch size, packed with 10 pieces, and costs 550 yen including tax.

There is a wide variety of colors available, including krill, glow chart, clear glow crash, and isomed grooving crash.

Kibikibina-Go 2-inch will be a powerful weapon in light games thanks to its excellent design and diverse action.

Title: JK Weber Shrimp 2.8
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Weber Shrimp 2.8 inch is a soft lure targeting black porgy (chinus) and rockfish. The delicate design of the parts allows water flow to escape and creates a natural invitation, and even just placing it on the bottom creates a sensual action. It also contains a powerful flavor made from powdered shrimp flesh, and its outstanding fish attracting power will induce deep bites.

The body has little resistance, and does not interfere with sinking even at points with strong currents, making it easy to remove the bottom. It is 2.8 inches in size, packed with 6 pieces, and costs 550 yen including tax.

There are a wide variety of colors available, including Gripan Melon, Red Hala Devil, Grape Green Flakes, Red Gold Flakes, and Orange Gold Flakes.

The Weber Shrimp 2.8 inch is a lure that allows for an effective approach to your target due to its natural vibrations and powerful flavor.

Title: JK Rhythm Glove 3
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Rhythm Glove 3-inch is a soft bait with an overall volume greater than the previous 2.4-inch model, optimizing the balance between the distance and the tail, which creates clear vibrations.

This lure is highly versatile for a wide range of rigs and applications, including jig heads, Texas rigs, Carolina rigs, Drop shot rigs, and rubber jig trailers.

The 3-inch rhythm gloves are available in a pack of 5, with the recommended offset hook size #2 and 1.

There are a wide variety of colors available, including solid black, green pumpkin pepper, SK Gripan/Pearl, Dark Thunder/Clear Silver, Chart Back Black, Cola Bluegill, Gripan Goby, Prism Shad, and Kwase Shad.

The 3-inch rhythm glove is a reliable lure that can be used in a variety of situations thanks to its high basic design and versatility.

Title: JK Rhythm Glove 2.4
Body (HTML):
Jackal's Rhythm Glove 2.4 inch is a compact, soft bait that is specialized for feeding. We thoroughly examine the thickness of the body, size and shape of the tail, achieving sufficient distance and stable action with no sinker. Even when you use graving buzz or fast winding on the surface, the body does not rotate and maintains a stable swimming experience.

This lure is highly versatile for a wide range of rigs and applications, including jig heads, Texas rigs, Carolina rigs, Drop shot rigs, and rubber jig trailers. It can be used effectively for both shore and boat fishing.

The 2.4-inch rhythm glove is available in a pack of 5, with the recommended offset hook size #2 and 1.

There are a wide variety of colors available, including Green Pumpkin Pepper, SK Gripan/Pearl, Dark Thunder/Clear Silver, Chart Back Black, Cola Bluegill, Dark Cinnamon Blue Flake, Gripan Goby, Pink Back Gold, Prism Shad, and Kwase Shad.

The 2.4-inch rhythm glove is a reliable lure that can be used in a variety of situations thanks to its high basic design and versatility.
